User_Message: What the f*** is PrEP, and why the hell should I care?
Response:
PrEP stands for pre-exposure prophylaxis. It is a medicine that helps prevent HIV. If you are at risk for HIV, taking PrEP can lower your chances of getting it.

You should care because knowing about PrEP can help you make informed choices about your health. It is an option to stay safe while being sexually active or if you inject drugs. If you have questions or want to learn more, feel free to ask!
